Package: bodycompref
Type: Package
Title: Reference values for CT-based body composition
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  person(given = "J. Peter",
         family = "Marquardt",
         role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "peter@kmarquardt.de",
         comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5596-1357"))
Maintainer: J. Peter Marquardt <peter@kmarquardt.de>
Description: Tool to get z-scores, percentiles, absolute values, and percent of predicted of a reference cohort.
    Reference values for skeletal muscle based on Tonnesen et al, Investigative Radiology, 2023 (doi).
    Reference values for adipose tissue based on Marquardt et al, 2023 (doi).
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
  assertthat,
  gamlss,
  stats,
  sae
